Module org.nasdanika.ncore
Package org.nasdanika.ncore

Interface GitMarker

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, Marker, Marker, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GitMarkerImpl
    public interface GitMarker
extends Marker
    A representation of the model object 'Git Marker'. Marker with Git information such as a map of remotes.

    The following features are supported:

    • Path
    • Remotes
    • Branch
    • Head
    • Head Refs
    See Also:
    NcorePackage.getGitMarker()
